    "description": "欢迎来到这款由单一开发者专门为虚拟现实打造的全新超凡脱俗的动作节奏游戏，在游戏中，你将按照节拍切割和射击，以击败异世界的威胁。沉浸于新的世界，感受每个跳动的原子中的音乐。用 Flextime 自由控制战斗的节奏。在专属的EDM音乐声轨中，按节奏锻炼身心，寻找星际之旅中隐藏的每一个秘密，成为声音和空间的终极传奇。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>光剑枪们</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884680/extras/290e7b22bd5b9f1178b07a391bdeb24a.poster.avif?t=1759691866\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884680/extras/290e7b22bd5b9f1178b07a391bdeb24a.webm?t=1759691866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884680/extras/290e7b22bd5b9f1178b07a391bdeb24a.mp4?t=1759691866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2>用未来的光剑枪们，在节奏中切割目标和spherombs，射击你的敌人！<br>这是第一款将两种令人兴奋的战斗风格融合在一起的虚拟现实游戏，呈现出令人心跳不已、无法阻挡的节奏动作。这是第一款将两种令人兴奋的战斗风格融合在一起的虚拟现实游戏，呈现出令人心跳不已、无法阻挡的节奏动作。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Flextime</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884680/extras/b78e4ddd465979ea59fa0a6c3046b580.poster.avif?t=1759691866\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884680/extras/b78e4ddd465979ea59fa0a6c3046b580.webm?t=1759691866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2>想要在摧毁一切的过程中增添一些&quot;黑客帝国&quot;风格吗？激活 Flextime（慢动作模式），减缓每一个敌人和目标，仔细规划你的下一步动作。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>场景关卡</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884680/extras/150dff2ae4840cb9755c3e8a3d68f2c0.poster.avif?t=1759691866\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884680/extras/150dff2ae4840cb9755c3e8a3d68f2c0.webm?t=1759691866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884680/extras/150dff2ae4840cb9755c3e8a3d68f2c0.mp4?t=1759691866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884680/extras/cb5be07ef1f45536af6af67cef48966d.poster.avif?t=1759691866\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884680/extras/cb5be07ef1f45536af6af67cef48966d.webm?t=1759691866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884680/extras/cb5be07ef1f45536af6af67cef48966d.mp4?t=1759691866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2>在19首歌曲中，提供5种不同的难度供您挑战，这意味着每位传奇或正在训练中的传奇都能找到适合自己的内容。您还可以选择在超过31个环境中实现个人动作电影场景幻想，其中一些可能会让您感到熟悉！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>健身</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884680/extras/33f1776eb7898edd3ea307a141aa16dc.poster.avif?t=1759691866\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884680/extras/33f1776eb7898edd3ea307a141aa16dc.webm?t=1759691866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2>用SolarBlack来保持健身！想要在您的虚拟现实健身游戏库中增加一款游戏吗？无需再寻找，因为SolarBlack拥有专为您定制的健身模式！充分利用我们的健身模式，在来袭目标上使劲出拳吧！它不仅能帮您获得最高分，还保证让您出一身汗。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>原创分数</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2>一位独立开发者的巅峰之作。拥有13首独特的原声配乐，专门为配合最先进的图像和氛围世界而作，与节奏同步跳动。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成就与可收集物品</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884680/extras/981bc0f51248115714910258e6b22164.poster.avif?t=1759691866\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884680/extras/981bc0f51248115714910258e6b22164.webm?t=1759691866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2>射击敌人、切割目标和躲避激光的组合对您来说还不够具有挑战性吗？除了射击敌人、切割目标和躲避激光之外，在游戏中尝试寻找所有可收集物品... 如果一切变得过于压倒，记住，您还有缓慢动作超能力：Flextime。",
